data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUC! Seller is VERY motivated- Just completely remodeled, but kept the classic feel of the original floorplan. 4 bedrooms plus study with floor to ceiling built-in wood bookcase, wood staircase, beautiful fixtures with high ceilings. 2 sided gas log fireplace facing dining room and master bedroom on main floor. Master bath has a steam shower feature. Just under 3 acres with pano views to the west. Little barn and workshop, huge finished garage and just enough easy landscaping. Vacant. This is a probate sale subject to court approval. Listing agent will provide details. Escrow  has been pre-opened with Sherry Ackerman at Stewart Title in Gardnerville.
